result.name: zostera-descriptions-north-norfolk-coast-cley-james-mccallum-1997
result.notes: Survey of the inter-tidal areas between Burnham Overy and Cley West Bank specifically mapping the distribution of Eelgrass, Zostera, species. Survey was conducted to locate the eelgrass for future monitoring. Maps were hand drawn with OS grid references included. Natural England id: NATENG000232
